headline: Jabil Links Sustainability Targets And AI Factories To Long Term Growth
summary: Jabil released its Fiscal Year 2025 Sustainability Progress Report, outlining progress on its five-year sustainability plan. The company expanded its AI-driven manufacturing collaboration with Arch Systems to deploy AI tools across its production footprint. These updates connect Jabil's environmental targets with its operational approach in electronics manufacturing.
